cu.error_type: unreachable elements or wrong routing definitions
cu.explanation_en: Changing the local S address to an unreachable subnet (10.0.0.5) will prevent the CU from binding to the correct interface, causing F1 setup failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting the transport S preference to an invalid enum 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and prevent proper transport layer initialization.
du.explanation_zh: 將傳輸 S 偏好設定為無效枚舉 'invalid' 會導致配置解析錯誤，並阻止正確的傳輸層初始化。
